<a id="技术栈"></a>
## 🛠️ 技术栈

*   **前端 (Frontend):** Electron, Vue 3, TypeScript, Pinia, Element Plus
*   **后端 (Backend):** FastAPI, SQLModel (Pydantic + SQLAlchemy), Uvicorn
*   **数据库 (Database):** SQLite (核心数据), Neo4j (知识图谱)

